{"tid":2042140,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"deliveroo香港個班外賣仔真係好丟香港人架","createTime":"2020-05-29T16:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T11:26:16.000Z","uid":5995,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7d750d8c1e3fea7a032f1097f0363c58d714038c","tid":2042140,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"Deliveroo罷工谷笑閪死我 難怪袋鼠職員post有人放風deliveroo要炒哂依排有份攪事既步兵<br />\n<br />\n今朝南亞谷問班香港外賣仔派唔派代表一齊上去同deliveroo傾<br />\n<br />\n成班香港外賣仔繼續好似之前唔出席罷工集會咁繼續失蹤 咁班南亞佢地自己單拖上去傾左3個鐘 最後咩都無傾成改善咁濟 但影哂大合照話已經同deliveroo傾掂數<br />\n<br />\n期後deliveroo職員post傳出話要炒哂依輪有份攪事既步兵(南亞全部車手唔關佢地事)<br />\n<br />\n成班香港外賣仔人地叫你一齊去又唔撚出席 依架成班狂屌南亞人過佢地一棟<br />\n<br />\n屌你老尾垃圾袋鼠外賣仔影衰其他外賣師<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hz5CvVR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhz5CvVR.jpg&h=44ad3807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaW96uy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaW96uy.jpg&h=52712ab7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf772cc795603e6d0297825a8d197771dd446cb3","tid":2042140,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa7194b4ffd205c2223bb4a17398e1c63dafcc7","tid":2042140,"uid":215621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:44:41.000Z","msg":"師兄跟得好貼"},{"pid":"e4cc1508c9ff47c980dd4f7ab34463127edb3da7","tid":2042140,"uid":5995,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"屌佢老尾<br />\n應該南亞人就變返舊制<br />\n香港人就新制 咁撚廢都有<br />\n要南亞人幫你班仆街爭取埋"},{"pid":"488677de2103179466b3ccc2181e9b13fa5fdb73","tid":2042140,"uid":273703,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:47:59.000Z","msg":"到底走入中聯辦果班係壞人定中共先係壞人呢？定成日拎呢樣野出黎攻擊人果班先係壞人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\"